Installation:

To install mtVarCaller run install.sh
chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh

Implementation

After installation mtVarCaller can be used to analyze data. mtVarCaller analyzes BAM files.For this purpose BAM file should be sorted and indexed. Put BAM file, index of BAM file and reference in same directory as follows:
mtVarCaller -r reference.fa -i sample.BAM

